@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api
@accessToken = paste_access_token_here
@eventId = paste_event_id_here
@galleryPostId = paste_gallery_post_id_here
@coverImagePath = C:\Users\User\Pictures\event-cover.jpg
@galleryImagePath = C:\Users\User\Pictures\fit.jpg

### List upcoming events
GET {{baseUrl}}/community/events

### Create event with JSON image URL
POST {{baseUrl}}/community/events
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Accra Thrift Pop-up",
  "description": "Weekend thrift market with local sellers.",
  "date": "2026-06-15T10:00:00.000Z",
  "location": "Osu, Accra",
  "coverImage": "https://example.com/event-cover.jpg",
  "type": "pop-up"
}

### Create event with cover upload
POST {{baseUrl}}/community/events
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=FormBoundary

--FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Accra Thrift Pop-up
--FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Weekend thrift market with local sellers.
--FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="date"

2026-06-15T10:00:00.000Z
--FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="location"

Osu, Accra
--FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="type"

pop-up
--FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="coverImage"; filename="event-cover.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< {{coverImagePath}}
--FormBoundary--

### Attend or unattend event
POST {{baseUrl}}/community/events/{{eventId}}/attend
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### List gallery
GET {{baseUrl}}/community/gallery?page=1&limit=20

### Create gallery post with JSON image URL
POST {{baseUrl}}/community/gallery
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/fit.jpg",
  "caption": "Sunday market fit.",
  "tags": "denim,vintage,accra"
}

### Create gallery post with image upload
POST {{baseUrl}}/community/gallery
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=FormBoundary

--FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="caption"

Sunday market fit.
--FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="tags"

denim,vintage,accra
--FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="fit.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< {{galleryImagePath}}
--FormBoundary--

### Like or unlike gallery post
POST {{baseUrl}}/community/gallery/{{galleryPostId}}/like
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
